12.000Z","msg":"我個人上會全力推廣仇恨黑警既概念<br />\n<br />\n無論黑警做乜都係有陰謀 唔會分析<br />\n無論黑警講乜都係大話 唔會分析<br />\n無論黑警有咩行動都係犯罪 唔會分析<br />\n無論黑警想做咩洗白都唔會原諒 只有死全家呢個結局 唔會分析<br />\n無論黑警係咪我自己既家屬 都會立即割席 我一齊死都無問題 唔會分析<br />\n無論係咩人支持黑警同情黑警都係我敵人 唔會分析<br />\n<br />\n我會慢慢提倡俾身邊人 教我既後代 再叫佢地宣揚出去 生生世世永不原諒港共黑警<br />\n落地獄啦你班仆街狗閪<br />\n<br />\n612 721 811 831 929 101 112 113 1111 1112 1117 1118 新屋嶺 還眼 還命 被自殺 實彈 周同學 陳同學 雞姦 強姦 輪姦 因姦成孕 中大理大之戰 人踩人 濫捕<br />\n<br />\n睇完呢串事件 連杯曱甴都做唔到嘅<br />\n唔好同人講你要光復香港 直接死咗去好過 唔好浪費地球資源"},{"pid":"659d6c379bddb00ec244bbc33747291a27d3af94","tid":1856653,"uid":213996,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T18:17:41.000Z","msg":"成班狗咁樣照住人仲大大聲話人破壞社會安寧 黑警死全家永遠係我心願"},{"pid":"493982b3cd75f43cdd9cf0917f57be2c3ecd13fb","tid":1856653,"uid":108631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T18:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e617580a4eea44288594a0d1ab1a241a8ea6d03e","tid":1856653,"uid":266289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T18:25:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">派利是啦</span>"},{"pid":"5441d68c7e06dffb6a6424dbd636e5ac7aeb7118","tid":1856653,"uid":181769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T18:26:07.000Z","msg":"利利是是<br />\n<br />\nBtw 感激肯堅定企出嚟嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88bec439f5665c9f9bbcbd85b2d8a742ebf21717","tid":1856653,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislik